        <updateDate>2011-01-27T17:04:17Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Detainee Trials at Gitmo Act - Provides that: (1) the detention facility at Naval Station, Guantanamo Bay, Cuba, shall remain in use indefinitely by the United States as a detention facility; and (2) any individual who is detained at Naval Station, Guantanamo Bay, Cuba, may only be tried by military commission which shall be conducted at Naval Station, Guantanamo Bay, Cuba.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
